Formula (all,i,PRIV)(all,j,REGHOUS)(all,r,REG)
    YH(i,j,r)=sum{m,MCOM,VIPM(m,i,r)}+sum{c,DCOM,VDPM(c,i,r)}
              +sum{t,TSSM,TSSMH(t,i,r)}+sum{d,TSSD,TSSDH(d,i,r)};

